text: The Electric Warlock Acid Witch Satanic Orgy Celebration Dispenser is the sixth studio album by Rob Zombie. It is a heavy metal album. It was released on April 29, 2016. Rob Zombie is a heavy metal singer. He wrote all of the music for the album with John 5, the guitarist that played on it. The album went to number six on the Billboard 200, an American music chart. It sold 40,000 copies a week after it released. It went onto music charts in ten other countries. == Track listing == == References == Category:2016 albums
